				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Equipment Advice Solicited 62nd level<a name="65865"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 6 04 6:34 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I personally found the boots more uselful, you can't always use selo's off the greaves (indoors).  Greaves on our server also more expensive (The Nameless).  With boots I did stalkers was making quite a good amount of loot off them they payed for themselves basically, so at least I lost nothing for buying them.  Also its an extremely easy way to get 3 FT, which is useful when you find yourself fading.
<br />

<br />
Because I got boots first the following occured:
<br />
Could solo for longer durations if not nonstop while waiting for a group in PoN and other zones.
<br />
Made more money off loot for longer durations of solo.
<br />
Gained the lvls/aa needed for fading memories faster than I would have with greaves.
<br />
Purchased them at something like lvl 58, or 57; by the time I was 65 the loot gained from being able to solo for longer durations payed for the boots.
<br />

<br />
However I think PoN ravenous diamond drop rate was nerfed or I have just been unlucky recently only pulling in a couple k now when I do a couple rotations.  Used to gain about 1k or more easily off 2 spawn rotations.</span></td>
