				<td colspan="2"><span>Concerning diamond drops off the Stalkers/WWs, I think the problem isn't that the drop rate was specifically nerfed; I think that SOE added <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=57995">Distrurbed Beast Essence</a> to the loot table.  This new item can take up a potential loot slot for whenever a diamond might actually have dropped before.  Daimonds still drop there, they just have to share the loot chances (dreaded RNG) with the new Disturbed Beast Essence drop.
<br />

<br />
It's a bummer, really, but, like I've said before, the game evolves.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
